{"tid":1511491,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中環羅富記粥麵個廚: 我係荃灣就拎刀斬暴徒","createTime":"2019-08-27T14:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T15:14:39.000Z","uid":276385,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b06b3f61b55a56af2f17b09a2a1c9109221a6c33","tid":1511491,"uid":276385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Hkvcs6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Hkvcs6.jpg&h=d5b4e6b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我好少寫食店劣評，但前日落雨入呢間舖食，<br />\n首先間舖店員就愛理不理，有個阿叔十問九唔應，結果個收銀係我地隔離唔耐煩叫阿叔先落到單，落單又要落漏單<br />\n間舖頭除左一般牛腩水餃麵，野飲得可樂，水要枝裝8蚊<br />\n我頂你咩知你係中環做遊客好好賺喇<br />\n<br />\n最頂唔順成班店員係度高談荃灣就遊行<br />\n女店員：我番到屋企......不過班人都唔知要搞幾耐。<br />\n負責碌麵的廚：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>佢地阻住你咪學Ｄ人拎把刀斬佢地囉，我係荃灣就會拎刀斬班暴徒。</strong></span><br />\n跟著又話：<strong>都唔知咩人選班搞亂香港出黎</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QkmFzGj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkmFzGj.jpg&h=94338268&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我咩都聽實晒 頂你個肺死黑店服務又惡劣<br />\n最緊要仇視香港市民<br />\n我唔上網公開你地惡行我對唔住自己<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"ca04c5dd6993b48809621fbd6d0354f191e4ebdb","tid":1511491,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6edeab14839d8e53e77d21f012ce65b40b2e3183","tid":1511491,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:20:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eb2f865ecdad9e2172ae6d1c7e93cc31516f7e5c","tid":1511491,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b06b3f61b55a56af2f17b09a2a1c9109221a6c33","tid":1511491,"uid":276385,"lik